                    <p class="mt-4 text-sm leading-relaxed text-gray-600">The Chancel Choir leads in worship each Sunday morning at the 10:30 a.m. worship service. This is our adult choir, and they rehearse from 6:00 to 7:30 p.m. on Wednesday evenings. This traditional choral group has a history dating back to the earliest days of First United Methodist Church. Within that traditional setting, we do a variety of choral anthems and works from Gospel to Classical in style.</p>
