                    </div>
                    <p class="mt-4 text-sm leading-relaxed text-gray-600">Celebration Choir is the children's choir, made up of elementary age children in grades 2nd through 6th. They rehearse on Wednesday afternoons at 3:30 and sing in worship on the fourth Sunday of each month. They are brought to the church via church vehicles, or parents are welcome to bring them. This group represents 7 different elementary schools in greater Texarkana. They join the Bethany Singers at the 5:00 p.m. Christmas Eve Service to lead the congregation in worship. A snack is served to them prior to the Wednesday rehearsal.</p>
